main event: A sighting of an unidentified object was reported in Denver, Colorado on September 3, 1956.
interesting points: The object's shape changed from elliptical to round.
The object had a very bright light.
The object was viewed visually and through binoculars for 1 hour and 10 minutes.
The sighting was observed by a civilian.
sighted object: An unidentified object with a changing shape and a very bright light
